English:
Retire this expedition and return ALL prisoners to the lobby

<size=90%>All collected artifacts will be accounted for.</size>
Description: "Expedition" is GTFO's word for "mission" or "map". "Prisoner" is GTFO's word for "player", because the player characters are prisoners.

French.Translation:
Met fin à cette expédition et renvoie TOUS les prisonniers dans le salon.

<size=90%>Tous les artefacts obtenus seront comptabilisés.</size>

Italian.Translation:
Annulla questa spedizione e riporta TUTTI i prigionieri alla lobby

<size=90%>Tutti i manufatti raccolti saranno conteggiati.</size>

German.Translation:
Diese Expedition aufgeben und ALLE Gefangenen zur Lobby zurückschicken.

<size=90%>Alle gesammelten Artefakte werden berücksichtigt.</size>

Spanish.Translation:
Retírate de la expedición y devuelve a la sala a TODOS los prisioneros

<size=90%>Conseguirás todos los artefactos reunidos.</size>

Russian.Translation:
Вы завершите экспедицию. Все заключенные окажутся в лобби.

<size=90%>Все собранные артефакты сохранятся.</size>

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation:
Retire-se desta expedição e devolva TODOS os prisioneiros ao lobby

<size=90%>Todos os artefatos coletados serão contabilizados.</size>

Polish.Translation:
Wycofaj ekspedycję i przenieś WSZYSTKICH więźniów do lobby

<size=90%>Wszystkie zebrane artefakty zostaną rozliczone.</size>

Japanese.Translation:
このエクスペディションを中止して全ての囚人をロビーに戻します

<size=90%>収集したアーティファクトは全て保有されます。</size>

Korean.Translation:
이 탐사에서 후퇴하고 모든 수감자를 로비로 돌려보냅니다

<size=90%>수집한 아티팩트는 모두 반영됩니다.</size>

Chinese_Traditional.Translation:
退出這次遠征並將「所有」囚犯送回大廳

<size=90%>將會清點所有收集的寶物。</size>

Chinese_Simplified.Translation:
退出此任务并送所有囚犯回大厅

<size=90%>将计入收集的所有红晶。</size>

name: MainMenu.MenuBar.RetireToLobbyDescription
